        "subject": "LU-7173 ldlm: do not grant intent-only lock",
        "message": "LU-7173 ldlm: do not grant intent-only lock\n\nIn ldlm_process_inodebits_lock(), do not grant intent-only lock\non lock server side, ldlm_lock_enqueue() could destroy it right\naway, presuming that it's intent-only and expecting it no granted.\n\nAdd debug message for this case and if it is shown, it is confirmed\nthen.\n\nSigned-off-by: Bobi Jam <bobijam.xu@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I9cb5095779284e0f99b0a8b31e2178b354d3a233\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
